                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7673" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0174</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4811 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“左右为难”到“左右逢源”: D公司订单农业供应链困境破解之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From “Dilemma” to “Success”: The Solution to  Company D’s Supply Chain Dilemma in Contract Farming</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李万福，许睿，徐周，万润钰，黄炜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福州万顺和贸易有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">订单农业；供应链脆弱性；供应链韧性；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Contract Farming; Supply Chain Vulnerability; Supply Chain Resilience.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">订单农业供应链往往涉及上游农户、焦点企业与下游商超，对于夹在农户与商超之间的焦点企业而言，往往是前有“农户违约”缕缕不绝、后有“商超退货”频频发生，时常处于“左右为难”的境地。如何破解这一订单农业供应链困境，使焦点企业实现从“左右为难”到“左右逢源”的转型，是应对订单农业供应链脆弱性的关键所在。本案例回顾了订单农业供应链焦点企业D公司的丹东草莓同时遭遇“大量农户违约”与“商超大额退货”两面夹击的事件，以及在该事件中暴露的D公司加工效率低下等问题，剖析了D公司陷入“左右为难”困境的症结所在，再现了D公司如何对症下药破解这一困境进而迈向“左右逢源”的辛路历程。本案例旨在引导学员理解及掌握D公司订单农业供应链“左右为难”困境的破解之道，并思考提升订单农业供应链韧性的可行之法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The supply chain of contract farming often involves upstream farmers, focal enterprises and downstream supermarkets. For the focus of the enterprise between farmers and super, is often in a dilemma that is farmer default strands of endless, followed by supermarkets returns occur frequently. How to crack this contract farming supply chain dilemma, so that the focus of the enterprise to achieve the transition from “dilemma” to “success”, is the key to addressing supply chain vulnerabilities in contract farming. This case reviews the incident in which Dandong strawberries of Company D, as the focal company of the contract farming supply chain, were attacked by “a large number of farmers defaulting” and “a large amount of returns from supermarkets” at the same time, also points out the problems of low processing efficiency of Company D. This case analyzes the crux of the dilemma of company D, and reproduces how company D solves this dilemma and moves towards success. This case aims to guide participants to understand and master the solution to the dilemma of Company D’s contract farming supply chain, and to consider feasible ways to improve the resilience of the contract farming supply chain.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《内部控制与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链脆弱性、供应链风险管理、供应链韧性、供应链战略、供应链协同管理；采购与付款循环内部控制；销售与收款循环内部控制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
